ing_font_size":2,"card_description_font_class":"font-body","card_description_font_size":1.1}},"card_hgF4zN":{"type":"card","settings":{"icon_preset":"none","heading":"2. Tested","description":"And ensure that every camera we sell works the way it did when it came out of the factory decades ago.","card_heading_font_class":"font-heading","card_heading_font_size":2,"card_description_font_class":"font-body","card_description_font_size":1.1}},"card_WgCPJ6":{"type":"card","settings":{"icon_preset":"none","heading":"3. Guaranteed","description":"If for some reason your camera isn't in tip top shape, it comes with a warranty. We replace or fix it no problem.","card_heading_font_class":"font-heading","card_heading_font_size":2,"card_description_font_class":"font-body","card_description_font_size":1.1}}},"block_order":["card_epFPVw","card_hgF4zN","card_WgCPJ6"],"disabled":true,"name":"Icon Card Row","settings":{"section_icon_preset":"none","heading":"The Brooklyn Film Camera Difference","subheading":"","heading_font_class":"font-heading","heading_font_size":3,"subheading_font_class":"font-body","subheading_font_size":1.3}},"176550325286c01233":{"type":"apps","disabled":true,"settings":{"section_layout":"normal","spacing_inner":"2","section_width":"max-w-page","color_scheme":"","spacing_top":"2","spacing_bottom":"2"}},"1756313365202a74cf":{"type":"apps","disabled":true,"settings":{"section_layout":"normal","spacing_inner":"2","section_width":"max-w-page","color_scheme":"","spacing_top":"2","spacing_bottom":"2"}},"977cac03-4044-4567-8907-fa55103a47eb":{"type":"complete-the-set","blocks":{"collapsible_DYfCGt":{"type":"collapsible","settings":{"block_type":"collapsible","heading":"How we Refurbish Our Cameras","link":"","content":"<p>All of our cameras undergo <strong>extensive refurbishments<\/strong> before they’re offered for sale. Each body is carefully inspected for corrosion, rust, lubrication issues, stiffness, and other mechanical concerns. When needed and possible we perform a<strong> cleaning<\/strong>, lubricate and adjust mechanisms, and ensure every moving part is properly working.<br\/><br\/>Where needed, wires are re-soldered, and electronic circuits go through a<strong> electronic systems evaluation<\/strong> to confirm they meet standards.<\/p><p>We also complete<strong> light seal replacements<\/strong> to prevent light leaks and preserve image quality. Lenses are checked for fungus, mold, haze, and impairing scratches, and our lens technician performs full CLAs when necessary. Aperture blades are guaranteed to move smoothly, free of oil or debris, and calibrated for precise operation.<\/p><p>From top to bottom, every camera we sell is restored with care to ensure it performs beautifully and lasts for years to come.<br\/><br\/>You can view our whole process <a href=\"\/pages\/warranty\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Warranty\">here<\/a><\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_9xjNk9":{"type":"collapsible","settings":{"block_type":"collapsible","heading":"Warranty, Returns and Exchanges","link":"","content":"<p>You can view our whole warranty policy <a href=\"\/pages\/warranty-new-delete-old-when-swap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Warranty\">here.<\/a> Cameras come with a variable based warranty and are guaranteed working and fully refurbished. <br\/><br\/>Point & Shoot's come with a 3 month Warranty. <br\/><br\/>SLR's come with a 6 month warranty.<br\/><br\/>We accept returns on cameras in 14 days after sale with a 15% restocking fee. Returned items must be brought back to us in the same physical condition they got to you.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_pR4zmY":{"type":"collapsible","settings":{"block_type":"collapsible","heading":"Delivery & Pickup","link":"","content":"<p>We ship most orders same day, but our processing times are based on 2 day delivery. We delivery via USPS & UPS or whatever carrier you select. Most domestic shipments are delivered within 2-4 days.<br\/><br\/>It is always free to choose pickup in store and your item is typically ready within a few hours<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_fNwyft":{"type":"collapsible","settings":{"block_type":"collapsible","heading":"Grading","link":"","content":"<p>We offer two cosmetic grades for some of our refurbished cameras: <strong>A Grade<\/strong> and <strong>B Grade<\/strong>.<\/p><p>Every camera we sell is fully refurbished and mechanically reliable. The difference comes down to appearance. <strong>A Grade<\/strong> cameras are in excellent cosmetic condition, while <strong>B Grade<\/strong> models may show light cosmetic wear such as small scratches, minor dings, or faint rust spots that cannot be removed. These marks are never excessive and do not affect function.<\/p><p>Because of these surface imperfections, <strong>B Grade cameras are offered at a discounted price<\/strong>. Any cameras with heavier cosmetic damage are not listed for sale online—they’re reserved for flea markets or used for parts.<\/p><p>Even at the B Grade level, you can expect a camera that meets our high standards of quality and performance.<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["collapsible_DYfCGt","collapsible_9xjNk9","collapsible_pR4zmY","collapsible_fNwyft"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Technicals","content_heading":"Similar items","heading_size":"h5","content_type":"none","featured_image_aspect_ratio":"4\/3","open_first_collapsible":false,"flip_desktop":true,"flip_mobile":true,"section_width":"max-w-fluid","color_scheme":"","spacing_top":"6","spacing_bottom":"2"}},"multitile_KDV8BX":{"type":"multitile","blocks":{"tile_qpzFf7":{"type":"tile","settings":{"show_on":"both","column_factor":3,"row_factor":1,"color_scheme":"","gradient_background_color":"","tile_aspect_ratio":"1\/1","content_position_vertical":"justify-center","content_alignment":"align-center text-center","content_alignment_for_mobile":"start","media_position":"background","heading":"","heading_size":"h3","text":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"button--filled","video_exter